quran[8]{c,v,t}:
  7,88,"Ibikomerezwa by’abibone mu bantu be, biravuga biti “Yewe Shuwayibu! Rwose tuzakwirukana mu mudugudu wacu wowe n’abemeye hamwe nawe, cyangwa mugaruke mu idini ryacu.” Aravuga ati “Ese n’ubwo twaba tutabishaka (mwabiduhatira)?”"
  7,89,"“Mu by’ukuri turamutse dusubiye mu idini ryanyu twaba duhimbiye Allah ikinyoma nyuma y’uko Allah yariturokoye (kurisubiramo). Nta n’ubwo dukwiye kurisubiramo keretse Allah, Nyagasani wacu abishatse. Nyagasani wacu Azi buri kintu cyose. Allah wenyine ni We twiringira. Nyagasani wacu! Dukiranure n’abantu bacu mu kuri, kuko ari wowe mucamanza mwiza.”"
  7,90,"Ibikomerezwa byahakanye mu bantu be (bibuza abantu gukurikira Shuwayibu) biravuga biti “Nimuramuka mukurikiye Shuwayibu, rwose muzaba muhombye.”"
  7,91,"Nuko ubwo baba batewe n’umutingito, maze bahinduka imirambo bapfukamye mu mazu yabo"
  7,92,Ba bandi bahinyuye Shuwayibu babaye nk’aho batigeze baba aho bari batuye (kuko barimbuwe bose). Ba bandi bahinyuye Shuwayibu ni bo babaye abanyagihombo
  7,93,Nuko (Shuwayibu) arahindukira abatera umugongo aravuga ati “Yemwe bantu banjye! Rwose nabagejejeho ubutumwa bwa Nyagasani wanjye mbagira n’inama. None se ni gute naterwa agahinda (no kurimbuka) kw’abantu b’abahakanyi?”
  7,94,"Kandi ntabwo twohereza umuhanuzi mu mudugudu uwo ari wo wose (ngo ahinyurwe), maze ngo tubure guhanisha abawutuye ibizazane no guhagarika umutima n’indwara z’ibyorezo kugira ngo bicishe bugufi (banicuze kuri Allah)"
  7,95,"Nuko imibereho mibi yabo tuyihindura myiza, kugeza ubwo biyongereye baranakungahara, maze baravuga bati “(Ibi ni na ko byagendaga kuva kera kuko) abakurambere bacu bagerwagaho n’ibizazane ndetse n’ibyiza (bidatewe no guhakana).” Nuko tubagwa gitumo (tubahana) batabizi"